                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <div class="px-6 py-4 border-t border-gray-800 flex items-center justify-between bg-black">
                        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Showing 1 to 3 of 15 entries</div>
                        <div class="flex space-x-2">
